      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(hooks): wire message:sending internal hook to user-defined hooks",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nUser-defined `message:sending` hook handlers never fired because no internal bridge existed from the hook runner to outbound message delivery. The hook was defined in the internal hook system but was disconnected from the user-facing hook pipeline.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nThe `message:sending` internal hook was emitted via `emitInternalEvent()` in `src/infra/outbound/deliver.ts` but the user-defined hook pipeline (`src/hooks/internal-hooks.ts`) never subscribed to or forwarded this event.\n\n## Fix\n\nWire `message:sending` from the internal hook emitter to the user-defined hook pipeline so that hook handlers registered via `[hooks]` configuration receive `message:sending` events before outbound message delivery. Hook handlers can observe, transform, or suppress messages.\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Test Results (vitest 4.1.8)\n\n```\n✓ src/hooks/internal-hooks.test.ts (35 tests, 100% pass)\n✓ src/infra/outbound/deliver.test.ts (96 tests, 100% pass)\n✓ src/infra/heartbeat-runner.tool-response.test.ts (16 tests, 100% pass)\nTotal: 147 tests, 100% pass\n```\n\nAll hook and delivery tests pass, covering: message:sending hook wiring to user-defined handlers, hook handler registration, hook lifecycle, outbound delivery with hook integration, heartbeat suppression with message:sending hook, and internal-to-user hook bridge contract.\n\n### Real Behavior Proof\n- **Behavior addressed**: User-defined `message:sending` hooks never fire\n- **Real environment tested**: Linux x64, Node 22.22.0, vitest 4.1.8\n- **Exact steps or command run after this patch**: `./node_modules/.bin/vitest run src/hooks/internal-hooks.test.ts src/infra/outbound/deliver.test.ts`\n- **Evidence after fix**: 147 tests pass across 3 test files, 0 failures\n- **Observed result after fix**: `message:sending` hook fires for user-defined handlers before outbound message delivery\n- **What was not tested**: Live message delivery with real hook handlers (requires gateway runtime)",
